        </p>
        <p>
          When significant game events happen at a fan's owned location - goals, serves, captures, or other sport-specific actions - the NFT holder earns points. This creates a direct connection between real-world sports action and fan rewards, transforming passive viewing into active ownership.
        </p>
        <p>
